    </p>
    <ul class="flex flex-col gap-y-2">
    <li>
      <Link href="https://github.com/eliheuer/img2bez" class="hover:underline">img2bez</Link><span class="text-muted-foreground"> — Trace raster images to font-ready bezier outlines — Rust library and CLI tool.</span>
    </li>
    <li>
      <Link href="https://github.com/eliheuer/bezy" class="hover:underline">bezy</Link><span class="text-muted-foreground"> — A font editor built with Bevy</span>
    </li>
    <li>
      <Link href="https://github.com/eliheuer/runebender-xilem" class="hover:underline">runebender-xilem</Link><span class="text-muted-foreground"> — A port of Runebender from Druid to Xilem</span>
    </li>
    <li>
      <Link href="https://github.com/eliheuer/cairo-drawbot" class="hover:underline">cairo-drawbot</Link><span class="text-muted-foreground"> — 🎨 A GNU+Linux compatible fork of DrawBot.</span>
    </li>
    <li>
      <Link href="https://github.com/eliheuer/spoonbender" class="hover:underline">spoonbender</Link><span class="text-muted-foreground"> — Cross-platform UFO font editor, a fork of Runebender</span>
